prompt: Fast FPV flight into the dense Amazon jungle at sunrise. Sweep low across a clearing where a group of deer sprint gracefully, dust rising beneath their hooves. Skim forward, revealing zebras resting just 100 meters away, their stripes flickering in shafts of golden light. Bank left as a cheetah lifts its head and meows softly, eyes glinting. Glide deeper through towering trees where giraffes stretch toward the canopy, then roll past elephants bathing near a muddy riverbank.
